Class TC_meter

java.lang.Object
  drcl.DrclObj
      drcl.diffserv.Meter
          drcl.diffserv.TC_meter
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, DFConstants, ObjectCloneable, ObjectDuplicable, java.io.Serializable
public class TC_meter
extends Meter
implements DFConstants

This class implementes a three-color meter. it can operate in two modes, single-rate or two rate refer to RFC 2697, 2698 for detail

Version:
1.0 07/16/2000

Properties:

  • PBS: peak burst size
  • PIR: peak information rate
  • CBS: committed burst size
  • CIR: committed information rate
  • mode: can be signle rate or two rate
Author:
Rong Zheng (zhengr@ee.eng.ohio-state.edu)
See Also:
Serialized Form
